headline: Gary Guo Joins Trane Technologies as Chief Integrated Supply Chain Officer
summary: SWORDS, Ireland, November 18, 2025--Trane Technologies (NYSE: TT), a global climate innovator, announced the appointment of Gary Guo as Chief Integrated Supply Chain Officer, effective November 18, 2025. Guo will report to chair and CEO Dave Regnery as part of the executive leadership team and will oversee Trane Technologies’ global integrated supply chain, including manufacturing, procurement, logistics, environmental health and safety, advanced manufacturing technology and operational excellen
